cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image synthesis using deep neural networks and its applications to various tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization and regularization techniques, which are common in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks for pruning and continual learning, which are related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
